{"tid":1364151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾人以為今朝地鐵係做緊好事","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:51:10.000Z","uid":146958,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"836beaf20fae206af9193bf83f98d3a551caa7ef","tid":1364151,"uid":146958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"今朝東鐵線因為工程車事故<br />\n影響火炭往返大埔墟暫停服務<br />\n<br />\n同一個時間 林鄭出席科學園諮詢會<br />\n要前往科學園 大多數都會喺大學站轉巴士<br />\n（東鐵線另一可前往科學園 只有沙田可以轉過去 只係得一架巴士）<br />\n<br />\n但當兩個幾鐘前 林鄭無出席到<br />\n而相近時間 東鐵亦都回復正常服務<br />\n<br />\n地鐵就例牌經常出事故<br />\n但係又咁啱係林鄭出現嘅時候先嚟停服務<br />\n究竟係真有事故 定抑或係官商勾結呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ffc85df2a291cf62c817421c42d66ec39b7fb8","tid":1364151,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"新死線！<br />\n<br />\n【記住條formula】死線已定，728不排除升級！置頂！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n726 5點 交代上環元朗 針對黑警<br />\n728 2點 回應五大訴求 針對政權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70hg0QQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70hg0QQ.jpg&h=5f3b0a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEtPBpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEtPBpe.jpg&h=d22be929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vuBph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vuBph.jpg&h=f992e9fe&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}